Start
  ↓
Upload Test Results Slice
  ↓
Receive Task ID
  ↓
Check Task Status Immediately
  ↓
 ┌─────────────────────────────────────┐
 │ Task Status = SUCCESS?               │
 └─────────────────────────────────────┘
          ↓ Yes                         ↓ No
       Proceed                       Check Status Again
                                      (Retry 5 times)

          ↓ After 5 Retries
 ┌─────────────────────────────────────┐
 │ Task Status = RUNNING?               │
 └─────────────────────────────────────┘
          ↓ Yes                         ↓ No (FAILED / ERROR)
  Save Task ID for Later Tracking      Raise Error Immediately

          ↓
Proceed with Next Upload Slice
          ↓
Once All Slices Uploaded
          ↓
Check All Saved Running Tasks
          ↓
 ┌─────────────────────────────────────┐
 │ Task Completes in 10 Minutes?         │
 └─────────────────────────────────────┘
          ↓ Yes                         ↓ No
       Proceed                      Raise Timeout Error

          ↓
Update Backlog Coverage (Link JIRA)
          ↓
Finish
